PN,30501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781053389
OL,3,CMillions unaware of available support
OL,4,Cwith household bills as debt soars `
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FMillions of households are missing out
OL,8,Fon support for essential bills such as
OL,9,Fwater, energy and broadband as their
OL,10,Fdebt to firms climbs to more than #7
OL,11,Fbillion, the public spending watchdog
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe National Audit Office (NAO) found
OL,15,Fonly a third of eligible broadband
OL,16,Fcustomers and 39% of water customers
OL,17,Fwho are struggling to pay their bills
OL,18,Fare aware of social tariffs, meaning
OL,19,Fthose who are vulnerable or on low
OL,20,Fincomes could be missing out on
OL,21,Fsupport to help manage debt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781053389
OL,3,CMillions unaware of available support
OL,4,Cwith household bills as debt soars `
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FThe report examined how Ofcom, Ofwat
OL,8,Fand Ofgem support consumers in
OL,9,Fvulnerable circumstances and whether
OL,10,Fpeople can access the help they need
OL,11,Ffrom providers of essential services.
OL,13,FIt concluded that regulators are not
OL,14,Faligning their performance
OL,15,Fmeasurements with actual consumer
OL,16,Fexperiences and outcomes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781053389
OL,3,CMillions unaware of available support
OL,4,Cwith household bills as debt soars `
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FWhile Ofgem and Ofwat had overseen an
OL,8,Fuptake in registration for company
OL,9,Fpriority services registers (PSR),
OL,10,Fconsumer awareness remained low, while
OL,11,FOfcom did not routinely monitor take
OL,12,Fup or awareness of support for
OL,13,Fbroadband customers.
OL,15,FThe watchdog said there had been a
OL,16,Fmarked increase in household energy
OL,17,Fdebt following Russia's invasion of
OL,18,FUkraine, rising by 118% since 2021.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781053389
OL,3,CMillions unaware of available support
OL,4,Cwith household bills as debt soars `
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FEnergy customers on supportive
OL,8,Frepayment plans owed around #1,000
OL,9,Fless than those without one in place,
OL,10,Fthe NAO found.
OL,12,FThe NAO found regulators had
OL,13,Fstrengthened protections since its
OL,14,Flast report in 2019, introducing new
OL,15,Frules on how companies treated
OL,16,Fcustomers and taking enforcement
OL,17,Faction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781053389
OL,3,CMillions unaware of available support
OL,4,Cwith household bills as debt soars `
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FBut it said the regulators must now
OL,8,Fmake changes to keep pace with
OL,9,Fconsumer needs, finding that customers
OL,10,Fstill struggled to contact their
OL,11,Fproviders and were not always aware of
OL,12,Fsupport available to help manage their
OL,13,Fbills, such as social tariffs and
OL,14,Frepayment plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781053389
OL,3,CMillions unaware of available support
OL,4,Cwith household bills as debt soars `
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FIt has recommended that regulators
OL,8,Fincrease awareness of available help
OL,9,Fsuch as social tariffs, repayment
OL,10,Fplans and other support schemes and
OL,11,Ftackle the drivers of rising debt such
OL,12,Fas inaccurate billing, delays when
OL,13,Fpeople move home and barriers that
OL,14,Fprevent consumers from switching
OL,15,Ftariffs.
OL,17,FIt also called on them to improve how
OL,18,Fconsumers in vulnerable situations are
OL,19,Fidentified and supported, and to make
OL,20,Fbetter use of data-sharing across
OL,21,Fsectors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781053389
OL,3,CMillions unaware of available support
OL,4,Cwith household bills as debt soars `
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FGareth Davies, head of the NAO, said:
OL,8,F"Regulators have made progress to
OL,9,Fsupport consumers, but they're not
OL,10,Fkeeping up with the pressure now
OL,11,Ffacing millions of households.
OL,13,F"With debt rising sharply, it's more
OL,14,Fimportant than ever to make regulation
OL,15,Fwork so that people know what support
OL,16,Fis available and can contact essential
OL,17,Fproviders when they need to."
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781053389
OL,3,CMillions unaware of available support
OL,4,Cwith household bills as debt soars `
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,FChairman of the Public Accounts
OL,8,FCommittee Sir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown
OL,9,Fsaid: "Price volatility is now the
OL,10,Fnorm across much of the energy sector,
OL,11,Fand consumers are at the sharp end of
OL,12,Fthis.
OL,14,F"Debt to energy companies has more
OL,15,Fthan doubled since 2021, yet far too
OL,16,Fmany households are still not
OL,17,Freceiving or are even aware of support
OL,18,Fto manage rising costs.
OL,26,@qD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781053389
OL,3,CMillions unaware of available support
OL,4,Cwith household bills as debt soars `
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,F"Regulators have a critical role to
OL,8,Fplay, but today's NAO report shows
OL,9,Fregulation is still failing consumers
OL,10,Facross water, energy and broadband.
OL,12,F"It remains too difficult for
OL,13,Fconsumers to contact companies when
OL,14,Fthings go wrong, financial support is
OL,15,Fpoorly promoted, while basic billing
OL,16,Ferrors are pushing households further
OL,17,Finto debt.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781053389
OL,3,CMillions unaware of available support
OL,4,Cwith household bills as debt soars `
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,F"While Ofgem, Ofcom and Ofwat have
OL,8,Fmade some progress, they must now act
OL,9,Fwith far greater urgency to ensure
OL,10,Fconsumers get the standard of service
OL,11,Fthey deserve."
OL,13,FAn Ofwat spokeswoman said: "We know
OL,14,Fthere is more progress that needs to
OL,15,Fbe made to drive better outcomes for
OL,16,Fconsumers, particularly those
OL,17,Fexperiencing vulnerability and during
OL,18,Fsupply incidents.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@NO]uD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
