OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781053389
OL,3,CMillions unaware of available support
OL,4,Cwith household bills as debt soars `
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,F"Protecting consumers who need extra
OL,8,Fhelp remains a key priority for Ofwat,
OL,9,Fand we continue to work with Defra to
OL,10,Fimprove outcomes for customers in this
OL,11,Fperiod of reform of the water sector."
OL,13,FOfgem said: "Energy debt remains a
OL,14,Fmajor challenge, and we are taking
OL,15,Faction to reset how it is managed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@fO]uD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781053389
OL,3,CMillions unaware of available support
OL,4,Cwith household bills as debt soars `
OL,5,CNAO
OL,7,F"We continue to work with Government
OL,8,Fon a targeted Debt Relief Scheme to
OL,9,Faddress historical debt, alongside
OL,10,Freforming the process people follow
OL,11,Fwhen they move house and set up energy
OL,12,Faccounts to avoid debt building up.
OL,14,F"We are also challenging suppliers to
OL,15,Fdo more ` including prioritising
OL,16,Faccurate billing and early engagement
OL,17,Fto offer fair, affordable repayment
OL,18,Fplans, and ensuring they are meeting
OL,19,Fthe needs of the most vulnerable
OL,20,Fcustomers."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU|D@KO]
